http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: The Royal Regiment of New Zealand Artillery is the artillery regiment of the New Zealand Army. It is effectively a military administrative corps, and can comprise multiple component regiments. This nomenclature stems from its heritage as an offshoot of the British Army's Royal Artillery. In its current form it was founded in 1947 with the amalgamation of the regular and volunteer corps of artillery in New Zealand. In 1958 in recognition of services rendered it was given the title the Royal Regiment of New Zealand Artillery.

뉴질랜드 포병 왕립연대(영어: Royal Regiment of New Zealand Artillery, 약칭 RNZA)는 의 포병 연대다. 이 연대는 효율적인 행정 병과로, 여러 연대 부대로 구성될 수 있다. 이러한 특성은 영국 육군의 의 유산에서 기인한 것이다. 제2차 세계 대전 때 활약했던 여러 포병 연대가 1946년 1월 해체된 이후 다양한 정규 및 자원 포병군단을 통합하여 현재의 뉴질랜드 포병 왕립연대가 탄생하게 되었다. 1958년 이 부대는 "뉴질랜드 포병 왕립연대"라는 이름을 인정받게 된다.

The Royal Regiment of New Zealand Artillery is the artillery regiment of the New Zealand Army. It is effectively a military administrative corps, and can comprise multiple component regiments. This nomenclature stems from its heritage as an offshoot of the British Army's Royal Artillery. In its current form it was founded in 1947 with the amalgamation of the regular and volunteer corps of artillery in New Zealand. In 1958 in recognition of services rendered it was given the title the Royal Regiment of New Zealand Artillery.
